As an AI language model, I can provide a general observation about trends among kids in Argentina, but please note that individual interests and preferences can vary greatly among children. 

In recent years, many kids in Argentina have shown a growing obsession with technology and digital platforms. They are often highly invested in social media applications, video games, and online content consumption. With the rise of smartphones and internet availability, young people are increasingly connected to virtual worlds and spend significant amounts of time engaging with digital content. However, it is important to remember that this observation may not apply to every child in Argentina, as interests and obsessions can vary widely.
